{"tid":951561,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[少圖]DIY鬆弛熊盒蛋改造水晶球","createTime":"2018-12-22T12:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T17:12:59.000Z","uid":38383,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd09895832d4b9c514000dabb5cd0e55393d29a7","tid":951561,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:27:10.000Z","msg":"材料:<br />\n盒蛋<br />\n閃粉<br />\n萬能膠<br />\n蒸餾水<br />\n甘油<br />\n保護漆<br />\n<br />\n最近re ment出既盒蛋都好適合整水晶球 有好多款 PKM 姆明 鬆弛熊 之類<br />\n今次用左依款re ment最新既鬆弛熊歐洲旅行黎整 入面有款極光好適合聖誕節<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/22/201756_e4cce26d9d75fd6342c94153d28275d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2F201756_e4cce26d9d75fd6342c94153d28275d3.png&h=fc989446&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/22/201757_fcba5890307d67d6509f202497382f0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2F201757_fcba5890307d67d6509f202497382f0d.png&h=5c4643be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n噴唔噴保護漆都得 如果想佢襟擺d 或者反光好睇d 就噴d油性保護漆(消光/半消光) 要注意潮濕天氣唔好噴 會白化令成舊野白晒 同埋透明既配件都唔建議噴 <br />\n噴完要等兩日先乾 除非你有抽濕機<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/22/201829_83363d289275a55fdb56d458a1e15990.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2F201829_83363d289275a55fdb56d458a1e15990.png&h=266dfaa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n乾左再用AA膠固定佢地 避免搖搖下甩左出黎<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n痴落個底盤<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/22/201925_574a5bf0c7ddacf401568e31bba6cfae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2F201925_574a5bf0c7ddacf401568e31bba6cfae.png&h=5a4f8146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n圍住底盤同個樽既邊位吱一圈萬能膠 唔吱會漏水 跟住套埋個樽<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/22/201946_c6b6bea6299d550b68b3446029cdc972.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2F201946_c6b6bea6299d550b68b3446029cdc972.png&h=f6e6f221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意外發意AA膠送果條野幾FIT百得膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/22/201959_06a841bfdf83d50c8172b02de6d99012.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2F201959_06a841bfdf83d50c8172b02de6d99012.png&h=2df08660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.<br />\n我用指甲鉗剪埋個蓋既勾 唔整個極光落去了 我覺得會好睇少少<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/22/202015_58de147efab5ff1ba76266d22fb2e00d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2F202015_58de147efab5ff1ba76266d22fb2e00d.png&h=d46fbe2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.<br />\n加入蒸餾水可以滿d否則會好多氣泡(其他人話蒸餾少D雜質) 少量甘油 閃粉 <br />\n閂蓋後萬能膠圍邊防漏水<br />\n完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/22/202317_c3bf35e941071e567431bcc3740dc813.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2F202317_c3bf35e941071e567431bcc3740dc813.png&h=b3cc053b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後記:<br />\n其實我都係第一次整 一開始就衰左 遇到好多問題<br />\n1.第一件事痴左個底盤同樽 搞到d配件入唔到去 要重新買過隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/22/202331_93ccc6cf7d2383df574028df3de1b726.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2F202331_93ccc6cf7d2383df574028df3de1b726.png&h=95e25639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.買左好多閃粉 只有一種岩用<br />\n3.最後萬能膠圍蓋邊再痴落去 點知個蓋皮會甩 <br />\n樣衰左少少+一樣漏水+入左少少氣 最後普通閂完先圍邊就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好相認 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83c3bd89f501635a823a44138a98d38a5e56699","tid":951561,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:30:23.000Z","msg":"冇精 負評"},{"pid":"a9977f7f18f0aa8385540822293457e9963e6341","tid":951561,"uid":5020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:33:32.000Z","msg":"球呢？"},{"pid":"21e364d3c4cd54e15e7788229d285731a65284e5","tid":951561,"uid":196922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:39:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"515e90e7b04642a14c41efe072f6f8f9c54b2440","tid":951561,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"水晶呢?"},{"pid":"550d870de42e85c511feee4fb60bd4933db3e052","tid":951561,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"有咩用途？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37f3a866663a5c172ca1799d038eb1b52dbcd5f","tid":951561,"uid":38383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"550d870de42e85c511feee4fb60bd4933db3e052","tid":951561,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"有咩用途？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"製造垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41546e2ea92f0db381af626ce64ffdd8da66a98e","tid":951561,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"成個package嚟喎"},{"pid":"ec74f3252631c0818526f8e575f3c630285e4685","tid":951561,"uid":38383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41546e2ea92f0db381af626ce64ffdd8da66a98e","tid":951561,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"成個package嚟喎"},"cite